{"tid":504703,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"追韓星既女係咪大多數都冇乜腦","createTime":"2017-12-20T09:55:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-20T10:53:44.000Z","uid":96878,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ab3643e7c0a11f84c71ecdcf1f764dcb92b03ba4","tid":504703,"uid":96878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T09:55:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/20/173849_436bc1a0c08dcdeb57cd23093bc6f9c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F20%2F173849_436bc1a0c08dcdeb57cd23093bc6f9c2.jpg&h=c16849d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時真係唔想話你地班港女冇腦<br />\n但追韓星追到話個偶像係自己所有既支撐 可以追到命都唔要真係弱撚智<br />\n老豆老母日日仆心仆命賺錢養你地 比錢你地買演唱會飛 買CD 買紀念品 又唔見你地班港女對佢地好啲？相反為個三九唔識七既偶像要生要死 <br />\n<br />\n計我話 揀女朋友娶老婆真係唔好揀個追韓星<br />\n第時佢偶像死左 佢又跟住去死 你咁就冇左條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbf10ea954b9387318d1ec0d47f8e2e144e5b1a9","tid":504703,"uid":99640,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T10:14:44.000Z","msg":"點解連登仔諗野咁有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講到追星就一定對父母唔好咁<br />\n追星=唔孝順，唔留意時事，唔理香港未來？<br />\n咩邏輯"},{"pid":"c12de255384e442c2197381114243dce49c000ea","tid":504703,"uid":149566,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T10:17:27.000Z","msg":"有冇人發現追韓星嘅女通常都冇仔"},{"pid":"812b6841238092fb271cb8d6029b618c0267fdad","tid":504703,"uid":14265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T10:20:57.000Z","msg":"通常波大"},{"pid":"9b25a1fb2a554904fac13fcf54e07ec37d04bfa3","tid":504703,"uid":32906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T10:34:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>通常波大</blockquote><br />\n呢到係香港"},{"pid":"60fd6b8be6cb8560d1346514133a2d1dee302822","tid":504703,"uid":85819,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T10:35:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"189eaf6039e2642bbc71c344a414